How do I show someone I am minstering to that I genuinely care about them? genuinely caring about them
How do I show someone I am minstering to that I genuinely care about them? not only being there for them, since that's not really enough sometimes, but also by lifting them up when they fall in deep and violent waves
How do I show someone I am minstering to that I genuinely care about them? maintaining the eternal perspective needed to guide us to receive helpful revelation on how to serve my ministering people
How do I show someone I am minstering to that I genuinely care about them? persisting in our help for them, even if they do not get it at first
